						               													<description>Small Time Crooks is a 15 minute RPG Card game that blends narrative mechanics and strategy into a short and sweet heist experience.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Small Time Crooks works in three stages:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the 'Case the Job' phase, you'll gain intel on the target, letting you plan the best route. Then, during the heist stage, you'll break in, overcoming obstacles and reaching the score. Finally, in the escape stage, you'll race to one of the exits before the guards are alerted.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Small Time Crooks is a cooperative, GM-less game that uses targets, or pre-built locations with scores, to steal. The base game comes bundled with 10+ targets to rob, and players can also build their own.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
